726405f-d.title: Queens: Corona Avenue - Otis Avenue
726405f-d.text:
Corona Ave. (tracks thereon) west side, at and adjoining Otis
Ave. Views 2,3 and 4, show rear views of the J.H. Smith Shady Lake
farmhouse. (small delivery truck in rear thereof). View No. 1
shows the tree that stood in the rear of the house. See views
located as Corona Ave., west side, opposite Fifty-fourth Ave. for
more data.
Oct. 1928.
Views 2\&3 :Feb. 1925
View 4 1'ay 1926
Eugene L. Aymbruster Collection
